result.name: Yixin Restaurant

reviews.text: A Cantonese restaurant with long history. There are some impressive good old golden day dim sums n dishes, but u must know which ones to order. Friendly services though prices are in the high side.
Friend brought me there for birthday celebration and was blown away by the quality of the dishes. Best cha siu in HK!!!
Good traditional dishes and very good service
A nice place for food, quality of food is on the average and at reasonable price.

Good food but bad service. I had to wait for one hour for the first dish and another hour for the dessert. Not to mention i have pre-ordered all the dishes 2 days ago.  Totally not a good dining experience.

result.name: 益新美食館

reviews.text: 感受很一般，价钱是中高級路綫的，食物水準及服務態度不值这样的价錢
A Cantonese restaurant with long history. There are some impressive good old golden day dim sums n dishes, but u must know which ones to order. Friendly services though prices are in the high side.
메뉴전부 맛있어요ㅋㅋㅋ 미슐렌인지모르고 평점 좋길래 우연히 들어갔네요ㅎㅎ 거위요리도 괜찮았고 레몬치킨도 맛있습니다. 마파두부가 먹고싶어서 물어봤는데, 메뉴에 없는데도 해주셨네요(ㅠㅠ마파두부진짜jmt) 추천
屬於香港的傳統食肆之一，保持一貫的高質水準，特別是編排的套餐考慮周詳，款式與份量皆恰到好處。
